00001 /******************************************************************************
00002 * File      : postProcess_tria3.c                                             *
00003 * Author    : Carlos Rosales Fernandez (carlos@ihpc.a-star.edu.sg)            *
00004 * Date      : 01-09-2006                                                      *
00005 * Revision  : 1.0                                                             *
00006 *******************************************************************************
00007 * DESCRIPTION                                                                 *
00008 * Calculates potential and electric field at the required points, and stores  *
00009 * them in files 'potential.dat' and 'field.dat'. It also calculates the force *
00010 * on the dielectric interface if required and stores it in file               *
00011 * "force-mst.dat" and "force-mp.dat" for MST and multipolar approximations    *
00012 * respectively. Avoids calculations inside columns when present.              *
00013 * Works for linear interpolation in triangular elements (3-noded triangles).  *
00014 ******************************************************************************/

00039 #include "postProcessCol_tria3.h"
00040 
00041 int postProcessCol_tria3(unsigned int ANALYSIS, double *axis, double **XF,
00042                          double **Xinner, double **mNodes, 
00043                          unsigned int **mElems, double **vMatParam, 
00044                          double *vProbParam, unsigned int *vBCType, 
00045                          double **xCols, double *vB)
00046 {
00047     FILE *fE,*fF,*fP;
00048     unsigned int count, i, j, nOrder, nPointInside, nShape;
00049     double Eps, R;
00050     double Fcm[3], mPot[2], mE[6], Xin[3], Xcm[3], Xeval[3];
00051     double **Fce, **Xce;
00052 
00053     /* Initialize */
00054     Fce = doubleMatrix(nElems,3,1);
00055     Xce = doubleMatrix(nElems,3,1);
00056     switch(ANALYSIS){
00057         case(0):
00058             fprintf(file_log,"\n\tpostProcessCol_tria3(): ");
00059             fprintf(file_log,"doing potential calculation...");
00060             fP = fopen("potential.dat","w");
00061             fprintf(fP,"#x\t\ty\t\tz\t\tRe[Pot(x,y,z)]\tIm[Pot(x,y,z)]\n");
00062             break;
00063         case(1):
00064             fprintf(file_log,"\n\tpostProcessCol_tria3(): ");
00065             fprintf(file_log,"doing field calculation...");
00066             fE = fopen("field.dat","w");
00067             fprintf(fE,"#x\t\ty\t\tz\t\tRe[Ex(x,y,z)]\tIm[Ex(x,y,z)]\tRe[Ey(x,y,z)]");
00068             fprintf(fE,"\tIm[Ey(x,y,z)]\tRe[Ez(x,y,z)]\tIm[Ez(x,y,z)]\n");
00069             break;
00070         default:
00071             fprintf(file_log,"\n\tpostProcessCol_tria3(): ");
00072             fprintf(file_log,"doing potential and field calculation...");
00073             fE = fopen("field.dat","w");
00074             fP = fopen("potential.dat","w");
00075             fprintf(fP,"#x\t\ty\t\tz\t\tRe[Pot(x,y,z)]\tIm[Pot(x,y,z)]\n");
00076             fprintf(fE,"#x\t\ty\t\tz\t\tRe[Ex(x,y,z)] \tIm[Ex(x,y,z)]\tRe[Ey(x,y,z)]");
00077             fprintf(fE,"\tIm[Ey(x,y,z)] \tRe[Ez(x,y,z)]\tIm[Ez(x,y,z)]\n");
00078             break;
00079     }
00080 
00081     /* Electric field and potential values at the required points */
00082     for(i = 0; i < nInternalPoints; i++){
00083         Xin[0] = Xinner[i][0];
00084         Xin[1] = Xinner[i][1];
00085         Xin[2] = Xinner[i][2];
00086         mPot[0] = mPot[1] = 0.0;
00087         mE[0] = mE[1] = mE[2] = mE[3] = mE[4] = mE[5] = 0.0;
00088         
00089         /* Exclude points within the defined columns */
00090         count = 0;
00091         for(j = 0; j < nCols; j++){
00092             if(nColType == 1){
00093                 if(sqrt(pow(Xin[0] - xCols[j][0],2.0) + pow(Xin[1] - 
00094                 xCols[j][1],2.0)) > xCols[j][2]) count++;
00095             }
00096             else{
00097                 if((fabs(Xin[0] - xCols[j][0])> xCols[j][2]) && 
00098                 (fabs(Xin[1] - xCols[j][1]) > xCols[j][2])) count++;
00099             }
00100         }
00101         if(count == nCols) nPointInside = 1;
00102         else nPointInside = 0;
00103 
00104         if(ANALYSIS == 0){
00105             if(nPointInside) potential_tria3(Xin,mNodes,mElems,vB,mPot);
00106             fprintf(fP,"%le\t%le\t%le\t",Xin[0],Xin[1],Xin[2]);
00107             fprintf(fP,"%le\t%le\n",mPot[0],mPot[1]);
00108         }
00109         else if(ANALYSIS == 1){
00110             if(nPointInside) field_tria3(Xin,mNodes,mElems,vB,mE);
00111             fprintf(fE,"%le\t%le\t%le\t",Xin[0],Xin[1],Xin[2]);
00112             fprintf(fE,"%le\t%le\t%le\t",mE[0],mE[1],mE[2]);
00113             fprintf(fE,"%le\t%le\t%le\n",mE[3],mE[4],mE[5]);
00114         }
00115         else if(ANALYSIS != 4){
00116             if(nPointInside){
00117                 potential_tria3(Xin,mNodes,mElems,vB,mPot);
00118                 field_tria3(Xin,mNodes,mElems,vB,mE);
00119             }
00120             fprintf(fP,"%le\t%le\t%le\t",Xin[0],Xin[1],Xin[2]);
00121             fprintf(fP,"%le %le\n",mPot[0],mPot[1]);
00122             fprintf(fE,"%le\t%le\t%le\t",Xin[0],Xin[1],Xin[2]);
00123             fprintf(fE,"%le\t%le\t%le\t",mE[0],mE[1],mE[2]);
00124             fprintf(fE,"%le\t%le\t%le\n",mE[3],mE[4],mE[5]);
00125         }
00126     }
00127     if(ANALYSIS) fclose(fE);
00128     if(ANALYSIS != 1) fclose(fP);
00129 
00130     /* Calculate Fdep at dielectric interfaces if required */
00131     if(ANALYSIS == 3 || ANALYSIS == 4){
00132         fprintf(file_log,"\n\tpostProcess_tria3(): calling forceMST_tria3() ...");
00133         fF = fopen("force-mst.dat","w");
00134         Eps = vMatParam[0][1]*eps0;
00135         
00136         forceMST_tria3(mNodes,mElems,vBCType,vB,Eps,Fce,Xce,Fcm,Xcm);
00137         fprintf(fF,"#Xcm\t\tYcm\t\tZcm\t\tFXcm\t\tFYcm\t\tFZcm\n");
00138         fprintf(fF,"%le\t%le\t%le\t",Xcm[0],Xcm[1],Xcm[2]);
00139         fprintf(fF,"%le\t%le\t%le\n",Fcm[0],Fcm[1],Fcm[2]);
00140         fprintf(fF,"#Xce\t\tYce\t\tZce\t\tFXce\t\tFYce\t\tFZce\n");
00141         
00142         for(i = 0; i < nElems; i++){
00143             if(vBCType[mElems[i][0]-1] == 6){
00144                 fprintf(fF,"%le\t%le\t%le\t",Xce[i][0],Xce[i][1],Xce[i][2]);
00145                 fprintf(fF,"%le\t%le\t%le\n",Fce[i][0],Fce[i][1],Fce[i][2]);
00146             }
00147         }
00148         fclose(fF);
00149     }
00150     
00151     /* Calculate Fdep at particle centre using multipolar method if required */
00152     else if(ANALYSIS > 4){
00153         fprintf(file_log,"\n\tpostProcessCol_tria3(): calling ");
00154         fprintf(file_log,"forceMultipole_tria3() ...");
00155         nShape = 0;
00156         switch(ANALYSIS){
00157             case 5:         /* Dipolar Approximation (Order 1) */
00158                 nOrder = 1;
00159                 R = axis[0];
00160                 break;
00161             case 6:         /* Quadrupolar Approximation (Order 2) */
00162                 nOrder = 2;
00163                 R = axis[0];
00164                 break;
00165             case 7:         /* Octupolar Approximation (Order 3) */
00166                 nOrder = 3;
00167                 R = axis[0];
00168                 break;
00169             case 8:         /* Multipolar Approx Order 4 */
00170                 nOrder = 4;
00171                 R = axis[0];
00172                 break;
00173             case 9:         /* Multipolar Approx Order 5 */
00174                 nOrder = 5;
00175                 R = axis[0];
00176                 break;
00177             case 10:        /* Dipolar Approx for Homogeneous Ellipsoid */
00178                 nOrder = 1;
00179                 nShape = 1;
00180                 break;
00181             case 11:            /* Dipolar Approx for Single-shelled Oblate Ellipsoid */
00182                 nOrder = 1;
00183                 nShape = 1;
00184                 break;
00185         }
00186         fF = fopen("force-dp.dat","w");
00187         fprintf(fF,"#Xcm\t\tYcm\t\tZcm\t\tFXcm\t\tFYcm\t\tFZcm\n");
00188         for(i = 0; i < nFPoints; i++){
00189             Xeval[0] = XF[i][0];
00190             Xeval[1] = XF[i][1];
00191             Xeval[2] = XF[i][2];
00192             if(!nShape) forceMultipole_tria3(nOrder,R,Xeval,mNodes,mElems,vB,vMatParam,vProbParam,Fcm);
00193             else forceEllipsoid_tria3(ANALYSIS, nOrder,axis,Xeval,mNodes,mElems,vB,vMatParam,vProbParam,Fcm);
00194             fprintf(fF,"%le\t%le\t%le\t",Xeval[0],Xeval[1],Xeval[2]);
00195             fprintf(fF,"%le\t%le\t%le\n",Fcm[0],Fcm[1],Fcm[2]);
00196         }
00197         fclose(fF);
00198     }
00199 
00200     freeDoubleMatrix(Fce,nElems);
00201     freeDoubleMatrix(Xce,nElems);
00202 
00203     return 0;
00204 }
